{"tid":900430,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"請教各位絲打m痛會唔會返唔到工，返到又點有效止痛做野","createTime":"2018-11-13T08:26:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T05:57:38.000Z","uid":163291,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ad0d04040d0c4af09d8e76ab200ebeec50e8bef8","tid":900430,"uid":163291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T08:26:07.000Z","msg":"每次m頭一兩日都要食止痛，同標冷汗，唔係太集中到精神<br />\n最近唔知係唔係夜訓<br />\n有兩次會痛到係床典黎典去，嘴唇白哂，嘔埋<br />\n最近終於有工開喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想知各位絲打返工m痛心得<br />\n係唔係請假居多<br />\n返工會唔會用暖水袋之類"},{"pid":"172b0d65d652c2317a572a963f5a027ffc784cc8","tid":900430,"uid":170867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T08:30:53.000Z","msg":"食止痛藥啦 唯有係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我次次都會去到忍無可忍既地步先食 <br />\n但第二日個人會好攰 因為前一日太痛了 <br />\n完左period 就去睇中醫啦"},{"pid":"590b23b38c9d4778dd18223dc89fc4fb89e98fe8","tid":900430,"uid":163291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"172b0d65d652c2317a572a963f5a027ffc784cc8","tid":900430,"uid":170867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T08:30:53.000Z","msg":"食止痛藥啦 唯有係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我次次都會去到忍無可忍既地步先食 <br />\n但第二日個人會好攰 因為前一日太痛了 <br />\n完左period 就去睇中醫啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T08:45:29.000Z","msg":"我未到忍無可忍先食<br />\n大概覺得愈黎愈痛就會食<br />\n去到忍無可忍個時我多數已經扒低咗係床起唔到身<br />\n我諗遲下都應該睇下中醫 or 去照下check下個子宮<br />\n不過係office都係痛到pk點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 請假飛的返屋企？"},{"pid":"d6f8feddbbda36b1febb6f3d6d42dbb7edc15309","tid":900430,"uid":114370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T08:48:41.000Z","msg":"今日已經痛到要sick leave<br />\n我第一日會勁頭暈，仲會又屙又嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"857bc74af18543c93980e725a5ec8953dd36da84","tid":900430,"uid":174531,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T1